РАБОТА 16
Текст выполненного учащейся личного письма (с сохранением языкового оформления)
Chita, Russia
4 June 2012
C1.
Dear Tom,
Many thank for you nice letter. I was very glad to get it. I'm happy that you are ok.
So, i'll try answer your questions I like to travel too. I think that most beautiful water sights
in Russia is in Baikal Unfortunately, I have gone rafting but I really want to do it. To my mind,
extreme sports help people to relax, to feel something new.
What about you? Why did you choose Greece? How many days will you spend there?
Which cities are you going to visit?
Hope you hearing from you soon!
Best wishes,
Albina.
